<h1>Welcome</h1>

<p>I created this site to document the research I started in 2018.  At that time, I spent a lot of time taking classes on project management, UI/UX design, graphics design, mobile applications design, website accessibility, etc.  I discovered so many useful resources!  Hopefully these will be useful to others as well.</p>

<p>Beginning in 2021 I have decided to renew the focus on developing personal projects.  One of those projects is the redesign of this personal home page (new features, more functional layout, prettier appearance).  The <a href="https://www.sharonahamon.com/privacy">Privacy Policy</a> has been updated.  Broken links have been removed with the help of <a href="http://home.snafu.de/tilman/xenulink.html#Download">Xenu's Link Sleuth&trade;</a>.</p>

